title: Trouble In Paradise? NFL Week 5 Preview
description:
Welcome back to (debatable) with hosts Pablo Torre and Domonique Foxworth featuring Mina Kimes! On today's show: What does Draymond Green and Jordan Poole's dust-up mean for the Warriors? What are your thoughts on Tua Tagovailoa and the current state of the concussion issue in the NFL? What's the most interesting part about Victor Wembanyama's performances against G League ignite? Plus, we preview Cowboys vs. Rams and Bengals vs. Ravens!
